  <!-- Estrategias de acceso para estudiantes con discapacidades -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="accesibility-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Action and Expression: Internalize Executive Functions. Invite students to verbalize their strategy for showing more or fewer on their fingers before they begin. If students don’t mention a starting point of showing the number of dots on their fingers first, remind students that they can start there if it is helpful.</p>
    <p>Supports accessibility for: Conceptual Processing, Visual-Spatial Processing</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

